snippet.title: The Great Ace Attorney Chronicles - E3 Trailer
snippet.description:
The Great Ace Attorney Chronicles arrives on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, and Steam PC on July 27, 2021! 

Get to know fledgling defense attorney Ryunosuke Naruhodo, legal assistant Susato Mikotoba, and ace detective Herlock Sholmes in this new video first revealed at E32021!

#Capcom #TheGreatAceAttorneyChronicles #AceAttorney
